'''Pashi noodles''' was a macaroni dish cooked with boiled [[Water/Legends|water]].

In [[43 BBY/Legends|43 BBY]], [[Astri Oddo]] prepared this dish in [[Dex's Diner/Legends|Didi's Cafe]] for [[Jenna Zan Arbor]] and her party.

